divs: Sighting DetailsEarl saw different colored lights in a string, not blinking but in a sting in the sky to the southeast then just disappeared???? Not anything he has ever seen before, he is retired military and worked on the B1 and Flight line.........He just couldn't understand what it would have been??? We were just sitting on the back porch.......and he just noticed it.
